    <item>
      <title>泰国前总理领跑者在第一个法庭案件结案后重返议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/former-thai-prime-minister-frontrunner-returns-to-parliament-after-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最高法院清除了泰国反对派议员皮塔·林贾罗恩拉 (Pita Limjaroenrat) 违反选举规则的指控一天后，他重返议会，并发誓要审查包括数十亿泰铢现金发放计划在内的政府政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/former-thai-prime-minister-frontrunner-returns-to-parliament-after-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 06:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
